<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Salicaceae" genus="Populus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Populus tremuloides" order="Malpighiales" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="tremuloides">Populus tremuloides</taxonomicName>
, 8 Aug 2015, EB110-15 (MONT); Park County, Cinnabar Basin, under 
